data.description: The beautiful RC Chelsey plan from Rausch Coleman Homes is rich with curb appeal with its cozy covered porch and front yard landscaping. This two-story home features 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a loft, and a large family room. The kitchen is fully equipped with energy-efficient appliances, generous counterspace, pantry, and island. All bedrooms are located upstairs, including the master suite, which includes a walk-in closet. Learn more about this home today!
